<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Decisio Support & Privacy</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b0b12;
      --card: #141420;
      --text: #f5f7ff;
      --muted: #a7adc0;
      --accent: #7c6cff;
      --accent-2: #b9a8ff;
      --border: #24243a;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #090910 0%, #10101a 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 20px 64px;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 48px 24px;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(124,108,255,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(124,108,255,0.35);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .card p,
    .card li {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .cta {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent-2);
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 36px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .small {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="badge">Decisio Official</div>
      <h1>Decisio</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Smarter decisions with AI. Ask questions, compare options, and get fast guidance when you are stuck.
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="#support">Get Support</a>
    </section>

    <div class="grid">
      <section class="card" id="support">
        <h2>Support</h2>
        <p>
          Need help with Decisio? Contact us and we will get back to you as soon as possible.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@decisioapp.com">support@decisioapp.com</a><br />
          <strong>Response Time:</strong> 24 to 48 hours
        </p>
        <p class="small">
          You can use this page as your Support URL in App Store Connect.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>About the App</h2>
        <p>
          Decisio helps users make everyday choices with AI-powered guidance. Users can ask a question, compare two options, and use decision tools like roulette for fun or quick picks.
        </p>
